[OVERLAY] VimFu — ddp — Swap Lines Down
[SAY] {key:d}{key:d}{key:p} moves the current line down one. {key:d}{key:d} deletes the line, and {key:p} puts it below the next line.
[SAY] The cursor is on first. Type {key:d}{key:d}{key:p}.
